{"tid":1942840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度宣佈封城，所有商業停止，居民不準外出。泰國頒布緊急狀態宵禁。全球現有26億人行動受限制","createTime":"2020-03-25T09:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T13:43:08.000Z","uid":133680,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dae5b55c332c0dbb3a6856f330569c1d6b0c5784","tid":1942840,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200325/s00014/1585076259024/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%8326%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%90%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200325%2Fs00014%2F1585076259024%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%258326%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%25A1%258C&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=9387c7b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200325%2Fs00014%2F1585076259024%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%258326%25E5%2584%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%25A1%258C&h=e17bb890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200325/s00014/1585076259024/%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%8326%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%90%E8%A1%8C</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】印度總理莫迪周二宣布，由午夜開始全國「完全」封城21日，國民不能外出，所有商店、工廠、辦公室、市場、宗教場所關閉，水電衛生等必要公共服務將繼續，以遏止新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情。印度已有519宗個案，9人死亡。印度首都新德里等城市已下令封城至3月31日。法新社稱，加上13億人口的印度封城，意味着全球超過26億人行動被限制。英國、印度、法國、意大利及哥倫比亞均強制人民留家，不少國家亦實施宵禁、隔離或強烈建議國民留家。<br />\n<br />\n泰國緊急狀態 老撾失守<br />\n另外，泰國首相巴育周二宣布明天（26日）至4月30日全國實施緊急狀態遏制新冠病毒蔓延。頒布緊急狀態讓巴育政府有更大權力控制人流，實施宵禁，部署軍隊執法。惟政府亦可賴以加強審查傳媒，查封傳媒或個別建築等，惹人權觀察、反對黨等質疑政府借題發揮。<br />\n<br />\n至於泰國已累計錄得827宗確診，新增的106宗個案中，4人是醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n老撾昨日首有新型冠狀病毒肺炎感染個案，即東南亞國家全線失守。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/新華社）<br />\n（抗疫新階段）"},{"pid":"4b47a388cd4fc73aa3058a6000897873833b9148","tid":1942840,"uid":144626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:55:04.000Z","msg":"估唔到有生之年感受到咩叫Great Depression"},{"pid":"13cf890da65b2c5505e23d07c9525d5a755e7a22","tid":1942840,"uid":98289,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:55:36.000Z","msg":"支那成功建立人類命運共同體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0176d7aba7b1964f8d7307c39064afef951fae2e","tid":1942840,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c61de41a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png&h=26145686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png</a><br />\n印度泰國政府勿用激烈對抗態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"904e3aa2edd517e9d19a3b60161de9550f073814","tid":1942840,"uid":68689,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F777-11_jEwCa_1200x0.png&h=67503115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度泰國政府勿用激烈對抗態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17a8447d01e0cc754c13190af98adad24bed630b","tid":1942840,"uid":97277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:56:25.000Z","msg":"印度爆應該好難收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />